/target

# Local pre-consolidation backups. The consolidation merged 8 sibling
# repos into this workspace; if you keep `git bundle` snapshots of the
# pre-merge histories for recovery, put them here so they stay out of
# tracked history.
/pre-consolidation-backups

# Tool-local files Rust devs commonly leave behind.
*.rs.bk
*.swp
.DS_Store

# `otk-devcerts` default output dir. The tool's README warns explicitly
# against committing generated cert material (short-lived dev certs
# with world-readable private keys), but a workflow that runs
# `otk-devcerts --out ./dev-certs` from the repo root would otherwise
# leave the bundle visible to `git add -A`. Ignore both top-level and
# nested copies so per-crate dev sessions are safe too.
/dev-certs/
**/dev-certs/

# Default `storage_dir` for the shipped sample node configs
# (`timing-node/node-tls.toml`, `NodeConfig::default()`). The
# segment log is run-state, not source.
/data/
**/data/
